Package net.kuujo.vertigo.testtools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TestAckingFeeder
    A test feeder that tests that a message was successfully acked.
    TestAckingWorker
    A test worker that acks and emits all messages as children.
    TestFailingFeeder
    A test feeder that checks that a message was failed.
    TestFailingWorker
    A test worker that fails all messages.
    TestPeriodicFeeder
    A feeder that periodically feeds a network with randomly generated field values.
    TestResultCheckingExecutor
    A test executor that checks output against input.
    TestTimingOutWorker
    A test worker that times out messages.
    TestWordFeeder
    A feeder that feeder "random" test words to a network.
